snippet.textDisplay: We should truly applaud Coke studio on their (successful) representation of our beautiful culture. Kudos to you CS and to the entire team. How well they depict the diversity of Pakistanis is commendable without a doubt. Especially with this season, the inclusion of awesome singers from other ethnicities and the two transgender singers getting a chance just goes on to show that we, as a people, are defiant in the face of every wrong perception the world has of us. You go Coke studio, Live long and prosper. 👍
